{"tid":2352335,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"10港人判監至今未知安排  深圳禁境外者探監 北上家屬空等","createTime":"2021-01-04T03:27:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T03:32:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2aa670154b9255758c5e300f6a1883530e595974","tid":2352335,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T03:27:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210104/I2UOHFCMMNEUZD35SZURRVMSAM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210104%2FI2UOHFCMMNEUZD35SZURRVMSAM%2F&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyeDrFCZ%2FFQqiuLijmhCLlc8%3D&h=777af5f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210104%2FI2UOHFCMMNEUZD35SZURRVMSAM%2F&h=a9409dd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210104/I2UOHFCMMNEUZD35SZURRVMSAM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n10港人判監至今未知安排 <br />\n深圳禁境外者探監 北上家屬空等<br />\n<br />\n【黑箱審訊】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：謝偉俊：12人是港府敵人<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】12港人案中三名家屬，昨日已抵深圳接受隔離檢疫14日，希望盡快尋求方法探監，惟深圳市司法局上月暫緩受理境外人員現場探監，有份協助港人家屬的大律師預料，港人家屬會被視為境外人員。被判刑七個月的「香港故事」成員李宇軒，他的妹妹早前接受訪問時透露，因擔心家人回內地的人身安全，所以不會探望哥哥，相信他會諒解和堅強面對餘下刑期。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Z8BlDOm5VxfRz4HofK2ihz8FRL8=/2214x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OFF27BZLDRC2ZDKSHNCKPBQVDI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZ8BlDOm5VxfRz4HofK2ihz8FRL8%3D%2F2214x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOFF27BZLDRC2ZDKSHNCKPBQVDI.jpg&h=968c3024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■銅鑼灣昨有街站呼籲釋放內地被囚港人等多名政治犯。<br />\n<br />\n12港人案上周於深圳鹽田法院宣判，10人被判囚七個月至三年不等，其。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/GYeINaAgq_yQBT1OGhS2w2MfWhY=/1707x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UWRIVMMZU5FSVJHF5EWHKASXRA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGYeINaAgq_yQBT1OGhS2w2MfWhY%3D%2F1707x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUWRIVMMZU5FSVJHF5EWHKASXRA.jpg&h=ebad5617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■李子賢家屬去年11月曾到吉澳放氣球，寄託思念。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李子賢母擬隔離後赴看守所<br />\n<br />\n李子賢父親昨午接受查詢時表示，太太與其他家屬昨早上10時許出發過關，但至下午約2時，太太傳來訊息指仍在內地關口排隊等候過關。他稱，根據內地最新安排，周二起由香港經深圳灣口岸入境深圳人士，除必須持有24小時內核酸檢測陰性結果證明，亦須出示14天集中隔離醫學觀察期間將入住的酒店預約確認單，故希望太太可昨日順利過關，以免多一重障礙。<br />\n<br />\n不過，深圳市司法局上。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n李子賢父親坦言，不掌握內地探監安排及兒子判刑之後安排等資訊，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n12人中的「香港故事」成員李宇軒，他的妹妹Beatrice早前接受訪問時透露，由於擔心家人回內地的人身安全，因此到大陸不會探望哥哥，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n知道哥哥被判囚七個月後，Beatrice指心情沒甚麼特別，因此案操控於中共政權手中，刑期由政權話事，「。。。。。。。。。」。"},{"pid":"19e6beb7236afe163101d3b8cfee568cce1be10e","tid":2352335,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T03:30:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29adc0db5f461130f8b3a38b5ece575c74e6d6d7","tid":2352335,"uid":148756,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T03:32:18.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}